## Usage

This skill is invoked via the Skill tool:

```
Skill(skill: "{{skill_name}}")
Skill(skill: "{{skill_name}}", args: "[arguments]")
```

Or via gateway routing:
```
/{{parent_plugin_name}} [natural language request]
```

